================================================================
Project context
================================================================

This work is a concept demonstration developed in 12 hours on
9 May 2026 by Team-6 (Özcan Orhan Demirci) for the İzQ
Hackability 2026 competition (Sustainability, AI, and Coding),
organized by İzQ Girişimcilik Merkezi (İzQ Entrepreneurship
Center).

See README.md for the full project disclaimer.

